hu: Tuple.min ((fun xi => dist xi x') ∘ u) > δ
argmax_le: min_dist_x u x' ≤ max_min_dist u
mp.intro.intro.intro
u ∈ {u | max_min_dist u > δ}
Goals accomplished!

inst✝: Nonempty α

    /-
    The set of iterations such that max_x min_(u i) dist (u i) x > ε₁ is included
    in a set of iterations that are outside of a specific ball. As `t` is a
    `ε₁`-cover of the universe, `∃ c ∈ t, x' := argmax_x min_(u i) dist (u i) x > ε₁ ∈ B(c, ε₁)`
    and thus, any point outside `B(c, ε₁)` is at least at `ε₁` away from `x'`.
    -/

  /-
  We define `f~` differently : we just want to ensure that it is maximized within
  `Metric.closedBall c (ε₁/2)`. This allows to show that it exists a `δ > 0` such that,
  for any `x ∉ Metric.closedBall c (ε₁/2)`, `|f~ x - f~ x^*| > δ`. The latter leads
  to a contradiction as the algorithm almost never samples in `Metric.closedBall c (ε₁/2)` and
  thus, cannot produce iterates that are `δ`-close to `f~ x^*`.

  Some results on `f~(c)`.
  1. `f~(c) = max f + (f c - min f) + (max f - min f)`
  2. `0 < (f c - min f) + (max f - min f)`
  3. `max f < f~(c)` (direct consequence of 2.)

not_sample_space: ∀ (n : ↑nstar), ε₂ < gε₁ n
t: Finset α
h_cover: Set.univ = ⋃ x ∈ t, Metric.ball x (ε₁ / 2)
N₁:= ⋯.some: ↑nstar
t_card: t.card = ↑N₁
c: α
c_in_t: c ∈ t
hc: ∀ (n : ↑nstar), ε₂ / (2 * ↑↑N₁) ≤ (A.μ f ↑n) {u | ∀ (i : Fin ↑n), u i ∉ Metric.ball c (ε₁ / 2)}
ratio_ε₂_pos: ε₂ / (2 * ↑↑N₁) ≠ 0
h_ball_not_univ: Metric.ball c (ε₁ / 2) ≠ Set.univ
f_tilde:= fun x => if x ∈ Metric.ball c (ε₁ / 2) then f x + 2 * (1 - dist x c / (ε₁ / 2)) * (fmax hf - fmin hf) else f x: α → ℝ
f_tilde_eq_outside: ∀ ⦃x : α⦄, x ∉ Metric.ball c (ε₁ / 2) → f_tilde x = f x
f_tilde_eq_inside: ∀ ⦃x : α⦄, x ∈ Metric.ball c (ε₁ / 2) → f_tilde x = f x + 2 * (1 - dist x c / (ε₁ / 2)) * (fmax hf - fmin hf)
c_in_ball, h✝: c ∈ Metric.ball c (ε₁ / 2)
isTrue
f c + 2 * (1 - dist c c / (ε₁ / 2)) * (fmax hf - fmin hf) = fmax hf + (f c - fmin hf + (fmax hf - fmin hf))

ε₁: ℝ
hε₁: ε₁ > 0
gε₁:= fun n => (A.μ f ↑n) {u | max_min_dist u > ε₁}: ↑nstar → ℝ≥0∞
antitone_gε₁: Antitone gε₁
ε₂: ℝ≥0∞
hε₂: 0 < ε₂
not_sample_space: ∀ (n : ↑nstar), ε₂ < gε₁ n
t: Finset α
h_cover: Set.univ = ⋃ x ∈ t, Metric.ball x (ε₁ / 2)
N₁:= ⋯.some: ↑nstar
t_card: t.card = ↑N₁
c: α
c_in_t: c ∈ t
hc: ∀ (n : ↑nstar), ε₂ / (2 * ↑↑N₁) ≤ (A.μ f ↑n) {u | ∀ (i : Fin ↑n), u i ∉ Metric.ball c (ε₁ / 2)}
ratio_ε₂_pos: ε₂ / (2 * ↑↑N₁) ≠ 0
h_ball_not_univ: Metric.ball c (ε₁ / 2) ≠ Set.univ
f_tilde:= fun x => if x ∈ Metric.ball c (ε₁ / 2) then f x + 2 * (1 - dist x c / (ε₁ / 2)) * (fmax hf - fmin hf) else f x: α → ℝ
f_tilde_eq_outside: ∀ ⦃x : α⦄, x ∉ Metric.ball c (ε₁ / 2) → f_tilde x = f x
f_tilde_eq_inside: ∀ ⦃x : α⦄, x ∈ Metric.ball c (ε₁ / 2) → f_tilde x = f x + 2 * (1 - dist x c / (ε₁ / 2)) * (fmax hf - fmin hf)
c_in_ball, h✝: c ∈ Metric.ball c (ε₁ / 2)
isTrue
f c + 2 * (1 - 0 / (ε₁ / 2)) * (fmax hf - fmin hf) = fmax hf + (f c - fmin hf + (fmax hf - fmin hf))

not_sample_space: ∀ (n : ↑nstar), ε₂ < gε₁ n
t: Finset α
h_cover: Set.univ = ⋃ x ∈ t, Metric.ball x (ε₁ / 2)
N₁:= ⋯.some: ↑nstar
t_card: t.card = ↑N₁
c: α
c_in_t: c ∈ t
hc: ∀ (n : ↑nstar), ε₂ / (2 * ↑↑N₁) ≤ (A.μ f ↑n) {u | ∀ (i : Fin ↑n), u i ∉ Metric.ball c (ε₁ / 2)}
ratio_ε₂_pos: ε₂ / (2 * ↑↑N₁) ≠ 0
h_ball_not_univ: Metric.ball c (ε₁ / 2) ≠ Set.univ
f_tilde:= fun x => if x ∈ Metric.ball c (ε₁ / 2) then f x + 2 * (1 - dist x c / (ε₁ / 2)) * (fmax hf - fmin hf) else f x: α → ℝ
f_tilde_eq_outside: ∀ ⦃x : α⦄, x ∉ Metric.ball c (ε₁ / 2) → f_tilde x = f x
f_tilde_eq_inside: ∀ ⦃x : α⦄, x ∈ Metric.ball c (ε₁ / 2) → f_tilde x = f x + 2 * (1 - dist x c / (ε₁ / 2)) * (fmax hf - fmin hf)
f_tilde_c_eq: f_tilde c = fmax hf + (f c - fmin hf + (fmax hf - fmin hf))
fma:= fmax hf: ℝ
fmi:= fmin hf: ℝ
sub_argmin_nonneg: 0 ≤ f c - fmi
h_cases: fma = fmi
pos
fmi < fma

f_tilde:= fun x => if x ∈ Metric.ball c (ε₁ / 2) then f x + 2 * (1 - dist x c / (ε₁ / 2)) * (fmax hf - fmin hf) else f x: α → ℝ
f_tilde_eq_outside: ∀ ⦃x : α⦄, x ∉ Metric.ball c (ε₁ / 2) → f_tilde x = f x
f_tilde_eq_inside: ∀ ⦃x : α⦄, x ∈ Metric.ball c (ε₁ / 2) → f_tilde x = f x + 2 * (1 - dist x c / (ε₁ / 2)) * (fmax hf - fmin hf)
f_tilde_c_eq: f_tilde c = fmax hf + (f c - fmin hf + (fmax hf - fmin hf))
fma:= fmax hf: ℝ
fmi:= fmin hf: ℝ
sub_argmin_nonneg: 0 ≤ f c - fmi
0 < f c - fmin hf + (fmax hf - fmin hf)

f: α → ℝ
hf: Continuous f
hf_nconst: ¬Constant f
ε₁: ℝ
hε₁: ε₁ > 0
gε₁:= fun n => (A.μ f ↑n) {u | max_min_dist u > ε₁}: ↑nstar → ℝ≥0∞
antitone_gε₁: Antitone gε₁
ε₂: ℝ≥0∞
hε₂: 0 < ε₂
not_sample_space: ∀ (n : ↑nstar), ε₂ < gε₁ n
t: Finset α
h_cover: Set.univ = ⋃ x ∈ t, Metric.ball x (ε₁ / 2)
N₁:= ⋯.some: ↑nstar
t_card: t.card = ↑N₁
c: α
c_in_t: c ∈ t
hc: ∀ (n : ↑nstar), ε₂ / (2 * ↑↑N₁) ≤ (A.μ f ↑n) {u | ∀ (i : Fin ↑n), u i ∉ Metric.ball c (ε₁ / 2)}
ratio_ε₂_pos: ε₂ / (2 * ↑↑N₁) ≠ 0
h_ball_not_univ: Metric.ball c (ε₁ / 2) ≠ Set.univ
f_tilde:= fun x => if x ∈ Metric.ball c (ε₁ / 2) then f x + 2 * (1 - dist x c / (ε₁ / 2)) * (fmax hf - fmin hf) else f x: α → ℝ
f_tilde_eq_outside: ∀ ⦃x : α⦄, x ∉ Metric.ball c (ε₁ / 2) → f_tilde x = f x
f_tilde_eq_inside: ∀ ⦃x : α⦄, x ∈ Metric.ball c (ε₁ / 2) → f_tilde x = f x + 2 * (1 - dist x c / (ε₁ / 2)) * (fmax hf - fmin hf)
f_tilde_c_eq: f_tilde c = fmax hf + (f c - fmin hf + (fmax hf - fmin hf))
sum_dist_pos: 0 < f c - fmin hf + (fmax hf - fmin hf)
f_tilde_c_gt_max_f: fmax hf < f_tilde c
cont_f_tilde_expr: Continuous fun x => f x + 2 * (1 - dist x c / (ε₁ / 2)) * (fmax hf - fmin hf)
a: α
a_in_frontier: a ∈ frontier (Metric.ball c (ε₁ / 2))

f_tilde_eq_outside: ∀ ⦃x : α⦄, x ∉ Metric.ball c (ε₁ / 2) → f_tilde x = f x
f_tilde_eq_inside: ∀ ⦃x : α⦄, x ∈ Metric.ball c (ε₁ / 2) → f_tilde x = f x + 2 * (1 - dist x c / (ε₁ / 2)) * (fmax hf - fmin hf)
f_tilde_c_eq: f_tilde c = fmax hf + (f c - fmin hf + (fmax hf - fmin hf))
sum_dist_pos: 0 < f c - fmin hf + (fmax hf - fmin hf)
f_tilde_c_gt_max_f: fmax hf < f_tilde c
cont_f_tilde_expr: Continuous fun x => f x + 2 * (1 - dist x c / (ε₁ / 2)) * (fmax hf - fmin hf)
a: α
ne_zero: ε₁ / 2 ≠ 0
a_in_frontier: dist a c = ε₁ / 2
f a + 2 * (1 - dist a c / (ε₁ / 2)) * (fmax hf - fmin hf) = f a

f_tilde_c_gt_max_f: fmax hf < f_tilde c

f: α → ℝ
hf: Continuous f
hf_nconst: ¬Constant f
ε₁: ℝ
hε₁: ε₁ > 0
gε₁:= fun n => (A.μ f ↑n) {u | max_min_dist u > ε₁}: ↑nstar → ℝ≥0∞
antitone_gε₁: Antitone gε₁
ε₂: ℝ≥0∞
hε₂: 0 < ε₂
not_sample_space: ∀ (n : ↑nstar), ε₂ < gε₁ n
t: Finset α
h_cover: Set.univ = ⋃ x ∈ t, Metric.ball x (ε₁ / 2)
N₁:= ⋯.some: ↑nstar
t_card: t.card = ↑N₁
c: α
c_in_t: c ∈ t
hc: ∀ (n : ↑nstar), ε₂ / (2 * ↑↑N₁) ≤ (A.μ f ↑n) {u | ∀ (i : Fin ↑n), u i ∉ Metric.ball c (ε₁ / 2)}
ratio_ε₂_pos: ε₂ / (2 * ↑↑N₁) ≠ 0
h_ball_not_univ: Metric.ball c (ε₁ / 2) ≠ Set.univ
f_tilde:= fun x => if x ∈ Metric.ball c (ε₁ / 2) then f x + 2 * (1 - dist x c / (ε₁ / 2)) * (fmax hf - fmin hf) else f x: α → ℝ
f_tilde_eq_outside: ∀ ⦃x : α⦄, x ∉ Metric.ball c (ε₁ / 2) → f_tilde x = f x
f_tilde_eq_inside: ∀ ⦃x : α⦄, x ∈ Metric.ball c (ε₁ / 2) → f_tilde x = f x + 2 * (1 - dist x c / (ε₁ / 2)) * (fmax hf - fmin hf)
f_tilde_c_eq: f_tilde c = fmax hf + (f c - fmin hf + (fmax hf - fmin hf))
sum_dist_pos: 0 < f c - fmin hf + (fmax hf - fmin hf)
f_tilde_c_gt_max_f: fmax hf < f_tilde c
hf_tilde: Continuous f_tilde
B:= Metric.ball c (ε₁ / 2): Set α
¬Constant f_tilde

f: α → ℝ
hf: Continuous f
hf_nconst: ¬Constant f
ε₁: ℝ
hε₁: ε₁ > 0
gε₁:= fun n => (A.μ f ↑n) {u | max_min_dist u > ε₁}: ↑nstar → ℝ≥0∞
antitone_gε₁: Antitone gε₁
ε₂: ℝ≥0∞
hε₂: 0 < ε₂
not_sample_space: ∀ (n : ↑nstar), ε₂ < gε₁ n
t: Finset α
h_cover: Set.univ = ⋃ x ∈ t, Metric.ball x (ε₁ / 2)
N₁:= ⋯.some: ↑nstar
t_card: t.card = ↑N₁
c: α
c_in_t: c ∈ t
hc: ∀ (n : ↑nstar), ε₂ / (2 * ↑↑N₁) ≤ (A.μ f ↑n) {u | ∀ (i : Fin ↑n), u i ∉ Metric.ball c (ε₁ / 2)}
ratio_ε₂_pos: ε₂ / (2 * ↑↑N₁) ≠ 0
h_ball_not_univ: Metric.ball c (ε₁ / 2) ≠ Set.univ
f_tilde:= fun x => if x ∈ Metric.ball c (ε₁ / 2) then f x + 2 * (1 - dist x c / (ε₁ / 2)) * (fmax hf - fmin hf) else f x: α → ℝ
f_tilde_eq_outside: ∀ ⦃x : α⦄, x ∉ Metric.ball c (ε₁ / 2) → f_tilde x = f x
f_tilde_eq_inside: ∀ ⦃x : α⦄, x ∈ Metric.ball c (ε₁ / 2) → f_tilde x = f x + 2 * (1 - dist x c / (ε₁ / 2)) * (fmax hf - fmin hf)
f_tilde_c_eq: f_tilde c = fmax hf + (f c - fmin hf + (fmax hf - fmin hf))
sum_dist_pos: 0 < f c - fmin hf + (fmax hf - fmin hf)
f_tilde_c_gt_max_f: fmax hf < f_tilde c

h: ∀ ⦃f : α → ℝ⦄ (hf : Continuous f), ¬Constant f → isConsistentOverContinuous A hf
f: α → ℝ
hf: Continuous f
hf_nconst: ¬Constant f
ε₁: ℝ
hε₁: ε₁ > 0
gε₁:= fun n => (A.μ f ↑n) {u | max_min_dist u > ε₁}: ↑nstar → ℝ≥0∞
antitone_gε₁: Antitone gε₁
ε₂: ℝ≥0∞
hε₂: 0 < ε₂
not_sample_space: ∀ (n : ↑nstar), ε₂ < gε₁ n
t: Finset α
h_cover: Set.univ = ⋃ x ∈ t, Metric.ball x (ε₁ / 2)
N₁:= ⋯.some: ↑nstar
t_card: t.card = ↑N₁
c: α
c_in_t: c ∈ t
hc: ∀ (n : ↑nstar), ε₂ / (2 * ↑↑N₁) ≤ (A.μ f ↑n) {u | ∀ (i : Fin ↑n), u i ∉ Metric.ball c (ε₁ / 2)}
ratio_ε₂_pos: ε₂ / (2 * ↑↑N₁) ≠ 0
h_ball_not_univ: Metric.ball c (ε₁ / 2) ≠ Set.univ
f_tilde:= fun x => if x ∈ Metric.ball c (ε₁ / 2) then f x + 2 * (1 - dist x c / (ε₁ / 2)) * (fmax hf - fmin hf) else f x: α → ℝ
f_tilde_eq_outside: ∀ ⦃x : α⦄, x ∉ Metric.ball c (ε₁ / 2) → f_tilde x = f x
f_tilde_eq_inside: ∀ ⦃x : α⦄, x ∈ Metric.ball c (ε₁ / 2) → f_tilde x = f x + 2 * (1 - dist x c / (ε₁ / 2)) * (fmax hf - fmin hf)
f_tilde_c_eq: f_tilde c = fmax hf + (f c - fmin hf + (fmax hf - fmin hf))
sum_dist_pos: 0 < f c - fmin hf + (fmax hf - fmin hf)
f_tilde_c_gt_max_f: fmax hf < f_tilde c
hf_tilde: Continuous f_tilde
B:= Metric.ball c (ε₁ / 2): Set α
x: α
hx: x ∉ B
intro
f x ≠ f_tilde c

f_tilde_eq_outside: ∀ ⦃x : α⦄, x ∉ Metric.ball c (ε₁ / 2) → f_tilde x = f x
f_tilde_eq_inside: ∀ ⦃x : α⦄, x ∈ Metric.ball c (ε₁ / 2) → f_tilde x = f x + 2 * (1 - dist x c / (ε₁ / 2)) * (fmax hf - fmin hf)
f_tilde_c_eq: f_tilde c = fmax hf + (f c - fmin hf + (fmax hf - fmin hf))
sum_dist_pos: 0 < f c - fmin hf + (fmax hf - fmin hf)
f_tilde_c_gt_max_f: fmax hf < f_tilde c
hf_tilde: Continuous f_tilde
nconst_f_tilde: ¬Constant f_tilde
x':= compact_argmax hf_tilde: α
∃ δ > 0, ∀ x ∉ Metric.ball c (ε₁ / 2), dist (f_tilde x) (f_tilde x') > δ

inst✝⁴: MeasurableSpace α
inst✝³: SeminormedAddCommGroup α
inst✝²: NormedSpace ℝ α
inst✝¹: CompactSpace α
inst✝: Nonempty α
A: Algorithm α ℝ
h: ∀ ⦃f : α → ℝ⦄ (hf : Continuous f), ¬Constant f → isConsistentOverContinuous A hf
f: α → ℝ
hf: Continuous f
hf_nconst: ¬Constant f
ε₁: ℝ
hε₁: ε₁ > 0
gε₁:= fun n => (A.μ f ↑n) {u | max_min_dist u > ε₁}: ↑nstar → ℝ≥0∞
antitone_gε₁: Antitone gε₁
ε₂: ℝ≥0∞
hε₂: 0 < ε₂
not_sample_space: ∀ (n : ↑nstar), ε₂ < gε₁ n
t: Finset α
h_cover: Set.univ = ⋃ x ∈ t, Metric.ball x (ε₁ / 2)
N₁:= ⋯.some: ↑nstar
t_card: t.card = ↑N₁
c: α
c_in_t: c ∈ t
hc: ∀ (n : ↑nstar), ε₂ / (2 * ↑↑N₁) ≤ (A.μ f ↑n) {u | ∀ (i : Fin ↑n), u i ∉ Metric.ball c (ε₁ / 2)}
ratio_ε₂_pos: ε₂ / (2 * ↑↑N₁) ≠ 0
h_ball_not_univ: Metric.ball c (ε₁ / 2) ≠ Set.univ
f_tilde:= fun x => if x ∈ Metric.ball c (ε₁ / 2) then f x + 2 * (1 - dist x c / (ε₁ / 2)) * (fmax hf - fmin hf) else f x: α → ℝ
f_tilde_eq_outside: ∀ ⦃x : α⦄, x ∉ Metric.ball c (ε₁ / 2) → f_tilde x = f x
hf_tilde: Continuous f_tilde
nconst_f_tilde: ¬Constant f_tilde
x':= compact_argmax hf_tilde: α
fma✝:= fmax hf: ℝ
f_tilde_c_gt_max_f: fma✝ < f_tilde c
fmi✝:= fmin hf: ℝ
f_tilde_eq_inside: ∀ ⦃x : α⦄, x ∈ Metric.ball c (ε₁ / 2) → f_tilde x = f x + 2 * (1 - dist x c / (ε₁ / 2)) * (fma✝ - fmi✝)
f_tilde_c_eq: f_tilde c = fma✝ + (f c - fmi✝ + (fma✝ - fmi✝))
sum_dist_pos: 0 < f c - fmi✝ + (fma✝ - fmi✝)
h_contra: x' ∉ Metric.ball c (ε₁ / 2)
fma:= fmax hf: ℝ
fmi:= fmin hf: ℝ
h✝: x' ∈ Metric.ball c (ε₁ / 2)
isTrue
f x' + 2 * (1 - dist x' c / (ε₁ / 2)) * (fmax hf - fmin hf) = f x'

fmi✝:= fmin hf: ℝ
f_tilde_eq_inside: ∀ ⦃x : α⦄, x ∈ Metric.ball c (ε₁ / 2) → f_tilde x = f x + 2 * (1 - dist x c / (ε₁ / 2)) * (fma✝ - fmi✝)
f_tilde_c_eq: f_tilde c = fma✝ + (f c - fmi✝ + (fma✝ - fmi✝))
sum_dist_pos: 0 < f c - fmi✝ + (fma✝ - fmi✝)
h_contra: x' ∉ Metric.ball c (ε₁ / 2)
fma:= fmax hf: ℝ
fmi:= fmin hf: ℝ
f_tilde_x'_eq: f_tilde x' = f x'
f_tilde x' ≤ fma
Goals accomplished!

f_tilde_eq_inside: ∀ ⦃x : α⦄, x ∈ Metric.ball c (ε₁ / 2) → f_tilde x = f x + 2 * (1 - dist x c / (ε₁ / 2)) * (fma - fmi)
f_tilde_c_eq: f_tilde c = fma + (f c - fmi + (fma - fmi))
sum_dist_pos: 0 < f c - fmi + (fma - fmi)
x'_in_ball: x' ∈ Metric.ball c (ε₁ / 2)
∃ δ > 0, ∀ x ∉ Metric.ball c (ε₁ / 2), dist (f_tilde x) (f_tilde x') > δ

hf_nconst: ¬Constant f
ε₁: ℝ
hε₁: ε₁ > 0
gε₁:= fun n => (A.μ f ↑n) {u | max_min_dist u > ε₁}: ↑nstar → ℝ≥0∞
antitone_gε₁: Antitone gε₁
ε₂: ℝ≥0∞
hε₂: 0 < ε₂
not_sample_space: ∀ (n : ↑nstar), ε₂ < gε₁ n
t: Finset α
h_cover: Set.univ = ⋃ x ∈ t, Metric.ball x (ε₁ / 2)
N₁:= ⋯.some: ↑nstar
t_card: t.card = ↑N₁
c: α
c_in_t: c ∈ t
hc: ∀ (n : ↑nstar), ε₂ / (2 * ↑↑N₁) ≤ (A.μ f ↑n) {u | ∀ (i : Fin ↑n), u i ∉ Metric.ball c (ε₁ / 2)}
ratio_ε₂_pos: ε₂ / (2 * ↑↑N₁) ≠ 0
h_ball_not_univ: Metric.ball c (ε₁ / 2) ≠ Set.univ
f_tilde:= fun x => if x ∈ Metric.ball c (ε₁ / 2) then f x + 2 * (1 - dist x c / (ε₁ / 2)) * (fmax hf - fmin hf) else f x: α → ℝ
f_tilde_eq_outside: ∀ ⦃x : α⦄, x ∉ Metric.ball c (ε₁ / 2) → f_tilde x = f x
hf_tilde: Continuous f_tilde
nconst_f_tilde: ¬Constant f_tilde
x':= compact_argmax hf_tilde: α
fma:= fmax hf: ℝ
f_tilde_c_gt_max_f: fma < f_tilde c
fmi:= fmin hf: ℝ
f_tilde_eq_inside: ∀ ⦃x : α⦄, x ∈ Metric.ball c (ε₁ / 2) → f_tilde x = f x + 2 * (1 - dist x c / (ε₁ / 2)) * (fma - fmi)
f_tilde_c_eq: f_tilde c = fma + (f c - fmi + (fma - fmi))
sum_dist_pos: 0 < f c - fmi + (fma - fmi)
x'_in_ball: x' ∈ Metric.ball c (ε₁ / 2)
f_tilde_max_gt_fma: 0 < f_tilde x' - fma
half_f_tilde_max_gt_fma: 0 < (f_tilde x' - fma) / 2
∃ δ > 0, ∀ x ∉ Metric.ball c (ε₁ / 2), dist (f_tilde x) (f_tilde x') > δ
Goals accomplished!

hf_nconst: ¬Constant f
ε₁: ℝ
hε₁: ε₁ > 0
gε₁:= fun n => (A.μ f ↑n) {u | max_min_dist u > ε₁}: ↑nstar → ℝ≥0∞
antitone_gε₁: Antitone gε₁
ε₂: ℝ≥0∞
hε₂: 0 < ε₂
not_sample_space: ∀ (n : ↑nstar), ε₂ < gε₁ n
t: Finset α
h_cover: Set.univ = ⋃ x ∈ t, Metric.ball x (ε₁ / 2)
N₁:= ⋯.some: ↑nstar
t_card: t.card = ↑N₁
c: α
c_in_t: c ∈ t
hc: ∀ (n : ↑nstar), ε₂ / (2 * ↑↑N₁) ≤ (A.μ f ↑n) {u | ∀ (i : Fin ↑n), u i ∉ Metric.ball c (ε₁ / 2)}
ratio_ε₂_pos: ε₂ / (2 * ↑↑N₁) ≠ 0
h_ball_not_univ: Metric.ball c (ε₁ / 2) ≠ Set.univ
f_tilde:= fun x => if x ∈ Metric.ball c (ε₁ / 2) then f x + 2 * (1 - dist x c / (ε₁ / 2)) * (fmax hf - fmin hf) else f x: α → ℝ
f_tilde_eq_outside: ∀ ⦃x : α⦄, x ∉ Metric.ball c (ε₁ / 2) → f_tilde x = f x
f_tilde_eq_inside: ∀ ⦃x : α⦄, x ∈ Metric.ball c (ε₁ / 2) → f_tilde x = f x + 2 * (1 - dist x c / (ε₁ / 2)) * (fmax hf - fmin hf)
f_tilde_c_eq: f_tilde c = fmax hf + (f c - fmin hf + (fmax hf - fmin hf))
sum_dist_pos: 0 < f c - fmin hf + (fmax hf - fmin hf)
f_tilde_c_gt_max_f: fmax hf < f_tilde c
hf_tilde: Continuous f_tilde
nconst_f_tilde: ¬Constant f_tilde
x':= compact_argmax hf_tilde: α
∃ δ > 0, ∀ x ∉ Metric.ball c (ε₁ / 2), dist (f_tilde x) (f_tilde x') > δ

h: ∀ ⦃f : α → ℝ⦄ (hf : Continuous f), ¬Constant f → isConsistentOverContinuous A hf
f: α → ℝ
hf: Continuous f
hf_nconst: ¬Constant f
ε₁: ℝ
hε₁: ε₁ > 0
gε₁:= fun n => (A.μ f ↑n) {u | max_min_dist u > ε₁}: ↑nstar → ℝ≥0∞
antitone_gε₁: Antitone gε₁
ε₂: ℝ≥0∞
hε₂: 0 < ε₂
not_sample_space: ∀ (n : ↑nstar), ε₂ < gε₁ n
t: Finset α
h_cover: Set.univ = ⋃ x ∈ t, Metric.ball x (ε₁ / 2)
N₁:= ⋯.some: ↑nstar
t_card: t.card = ↑N₁
c: α
c_in_t: c ∈ t
hc: ∀ (n : ↑nstar), ε₂ / (2 * ↑↑N₁) ≤ (A.μ f ↑n) {u | ∀ (i : Fin ↑n), u i ∉ Metric.ball c (ε₁ / 2)}
ratio_ε₂_pos: ε₂ / (2 * ↑↑N₁) ≠ 0
h_ball_not_univ: Metric.ball c (ε₁ / 2) ≠ Set.univ
f_tilde:= fun x => if x ∈ Metric.ball c (ε₁ / 2) then f x + 2 * (1 - dist x c / (ε₁ / 2)) * (fmax hf - fmin hf) else f x: α → ℝ
f_tilde_eq_outside: ∀ ⦃x : α⦄, x ∉ Metric.ball c (ε₁ / 2) → f_tilde x = f x
hf_tilde: Continuous f_tilde
nconst_f_tilde: ¬Constant f_tilde
x':= compact_argmax hf_tilde: α
fma:= fmax hf: ℝ
f_tilde_c_gt_max_f: fma < f_tilde c
fmi:= fmin hf: ℝ
f_tilde_eq_inside: ∀ ⦃x : α⦄, x ∈ Metric.ball c (ε₁ / 2) → f_tilde x = f x + 2 * (1 - dist x c / (ε₁ / 2)) * (fma - fmi)
f_tilde_c_eq: f_tilde c = fma + (f c - fmi + (fma - fmi))
sum_dist_pos: 0 < f c - fmi + (fma - fmi)
x'_in_ball: x' ∈ Metric.ball c (ε₁ / 2)
f_tilde_max_gt_fma: 0 < f_tilde x' - fma
half_f_tilde_max_gt_fma: 0 < (f_tilde x' - fma) / 2
y: α
hy: y ∉ Metric.ball c (ε₁ / 2)
f_tilde (compact_argmax hf_tilde) - f_tilde y > (f_tilde x' - fma) / 2

f_tilde_eq_inside: ∀ ⦃x : α⦄, x ∈ Metric.ball c (ε₁ / 2) → f_tilde x = f x + 2 * (1 - dist x c / (ε₁ / 2)) * (fmax hf - fmin hf)

inst✝⁴: MeasurableSpace α
inst✝³: SeminormedAddCommGroup α
inst✝²: NormedSpace ℝ α
inst✝¹: CompactSpace α
inst✝: Nonempty α
A: Algorithm α ℝ
f: α → ℝ
hf: Continuous f
hf_nconst: ¬Constant f
ε₁: ℝ
hε₁: ε₁ > 0
gε₁:= fun n => (A.μ f ↑n) {u | max_min_dist u > ε₁}: ↑nstar → ℝ≥0∞
antitone_gε₁: Antitone gε₁
ε₂: ℝ≥0∞
hε₂: 0 < ε₂
not_sample_space: ∀ (n : ↑nstar), ε₂ < gε₁ n
t: Finset α
h_cover: Set.univ = ⋃ x ∈ t, Metric.ball x (ε₁ / 2)
N₁:= ⋯.some: ↑nstar
t_card: t.card = ↑N₁
c: α
c_in_t: c ∈ t
ratio_ε₂_pos: ε₂ / (2 * ↑↑N₁) ≠ 0
h_ball_not_univ: Metric.ball c (ε₁ / 2) ≠ Set.univ
f_tilde:= fun x => if x ∈ Metric.ball c (ε₁ / 2) then f x + 2 * (1 - dist x c / (ε₁ / 2)) * (fmax hf - fmin hf) else f x: α → ℝ
f_tilde_eq_outside: ∀ ⦃x : α⦄, x ∉ Metric.ball c (ε₁ / 2) → f_tilde x = f x
f_tilde_eq_inside: ∀ ⦃x : α⦄, x ∈ Metric.ball c (ε₁ / 2) → f_tilde x = f x + 2 * (1 - dist x c / (ε₁ / 2)) * (fmax hf - fmin hf)
f_tilde_c_eq: f_tilde c = fmax hf + (f c - fmin hf + (fmax hf - fmin hf))
sum_dist_pos: 0 < f c - fmin hf + (fmax hf - fmin hf)
f_tilde_c_gt_max_f: fmax hf < f_tilde c
hf_tilde: Continuous f_tilde
nconst_f_tilde: ¬Constant f_tilde
x':= compact_argmax hf_tilde: α
δ: ℝ
δ_pos: δ > 0
hδ: ∀ x ∉ Metric.ball c (ε₁ / 2), dist (f_tilde x) (f_tilde x') > δ
h: ∀ ε > 0, ∃ N, ∀ n ≥ N, measure_dist_max A hf_tilde δ ↑n ≤ ε
N: ↑nstar
N_succ:= ⟨↑N + 1, ⋯⟩: ↑nstar
hN: (A.μ f_tilde ↑N_succ) {u | dist (Tuple.max (f_tilde ∘ u)) (fmax hf_tilde) > δ} ≤ ε₂ / (2 * ↑↑N₁) / 2
hc: ε₂ / (2 * ↑↑N₁) ≤ (A.μ f ↑N_succ) {u | ∀ (i : Fin ↑N_succ), u i ∉ Metric.ball c (ε₁ / 2)}
h_suff: {u | ∀ (i : Fin ↑N_succ), u i ∉ Metric.ball c (ε₁ / 2)} ⊆ {u | dist (Tuple.max (f_tilde ∘ u)) (fmax hf_tilde) > δ}
False

f_tilde_eq_inside: ∀ ⦃x : α⦄, x ∈ Metric.ball c (ε₁ / 2) → f_tilde x = f x + 2 * (1 - dist x c / (ε₁ / 2)) * (fmax hf - fmin hf)
f_tilde_c_eq: f_tilde c = fmax hf + (f c - fmin hf + (fmax hf - fmin hf))
sum_dist_pos: 0 < f c - fmin hf + (fmax hf - fmin hf)
f_tilde_c_gt_max_f: fmax hf < f_tilde c
hf_tilde: Continuous f_tilde
nconst_f_tilde: ¬Constant f_tilde
x':= compact_argmax hf_tilde: α
δ: ℝ
δ_pos: δ > 0
hδ: ∀ x ∉ Metric.ball c (ε₁ / 2), dist (f_tilde x) (f_tilde x') > δ
h: ∀ ε > 0, ∃ N, ∀ n ≥ N, measure_dist_max A hf_tilde δ ↑n ≤ ε
N: ↑nstar
N_succ:= ⟨↑N + 1, ⋯⟩: ↑nstar
B:= {u | ∀ (i : Fin ↑N_succ), u i ∉ Metric.ball c (ε₁ / 2)}: Set (Fin ↑N_succ → α)
hc: ε₂ / (2 * ↑↑N₁) ≤ (A.μ f ↑N_succ) B
C:= {u | dist (Tuple.max (f_tilde ∘ u)) (fmax hf_tilde) > δ}: Set (Fin ↑N_succ → α)
hN: (A.μ f_tilde ↑N_succ) C ≤ ε₂ / (2 * ↑↑N₁) / 2
h_suff: B ⊆ C
mono: (A.μ f_tilde ↑N_succ) B ≤ (A.μ f_tilde ↑N_succ) C
neq_top: (2 * ↑↑N₁)⁻¹ ≠ ⊤
refine_2
ε₂ / (2 * ↑↑N₁) ≠ ⊤

inst✝: Nonempty α
A: Algorithm α ℝ
f: α → ℝ
hf: Continuous f
hf_nconst: ¬Constant f
ε₁: ℝ
hε₁: ε₁ > 0
gε₁:= fun n => (A.μ f ↑n) {u | max_min_dist u > ε₁}: ↑nstar → ℝ≥0∞
antitone_gε₁: Antitone gε₁
ε₂: ℝ≥0∞
hε₂: 0 < ε₂
not_sample_space: ∀ (n : ↑nstar), ε₂ < gε₁ n
t: Finset α
h_cover: Set.univ = ⋃ x ∈ t, Metric.ball x (ε₁ / 2)
N₁:= ⋯.some: ↑nstar
t_card: t.card = ↑N₁
c: α
c_in_t: c ∈ t
ratio_ε₂_pos: ε₂ / (2 * ↑↑N₁) ≠ 0
h_ball_not_univ: Metric.ball c (ε₁ / 2) ≠ Set.univ
f_tilde:= fun x => if x ∈ Metric.ball c (ε₁ / 2) then f x + 2 * (1 - dist x c / (ε₁ / 2)) * (fmax hf - fmin hf) else f x: α → ℝ
f_tilde_eq_outside: ∀ ⦃x : α⦄, x ∉ Metric.ball c (ε₁ / 2) → f_tilde x = f x
f_tilde_eq_inside: ∀ ⦃x : α⦄, x ∈ Metric.ball c (ε₁ / 2) → f_tilde x = f x + 2 * (1 - dist x c / (ε₁ / 2)) * (fmax hf - fmin hf)
f_tilde_c_eq: f_tilde c = fmax hf + (f c - fmin hf + (fmax hf - fmin hf))
sum_dist_pos: 0 < f c - fmin hf + (fmax hf - fmin hf)
f_tilde_c_gt_max_f: fmax hf < f_tilde c
hf_tilde: Continuous f_tilde
nconst_f_tilde: ¬Constant f_tilde
x':= compact_argmax hf_tilde: α
δ: ℝ
δ_pos: δ > 0
hδ: ∀ x ∉ Metric.ball c (ε₁ / 2), dist (f_tilde x) (f_tilde x') > δ
h: ∀ ε > 0, ∃ N, ∀ n ≥ N, measure_dist_max A hf_tilde δ ↑n ≤ ε
N: ↑nstar
N_succ:= ⟨↑N + 1, ⋯⟩: ↑nstar
B:= {u | ∀ (i : Fin ↑N_succ), u i ∉ Metric.ball c (ε₁ / 2)}: Set (Fin ↑N_succ → α)
hc: ε₂ / (2 * ↑↑N₁) ≤ (A.μ f ↑N_succ) B
C:= {u | dist (Tuple.max (f_tilde ∘ u)) (fmax hf_tilde) > δ}: Set (Fin ↑N_succ → α)
hN: (A.μ f_tilde ↑N_succ) C ≤ ε₂ / (2 * ↑↑N₁) / 2
h_suff: B ⊆ C
mono: (A.μ f_tilde ↑N_succ) B ≤ (A.μ f_tilde ↑N_succ) C
half_lt_ε₂: ε₂ / (2 * ↑↑N₁) / 2 < ε₂ / (2 * ↑↑N₁)
measure_eq_f_set: (A.μ f ↑N_succ) B = (A.μ f_tilde ↑N_succ) B
ε₂ / (2 * ↑↑N₁) / 2 < (A.μ f_tilde ↑N_succ) C

f_tilde_eq_inside: ∀ ⦃x : α⦄, x ∈ Metric.ball c (ε₁ / 2) → f_tilde x = f x + 2 * (1 - dist x c / (ε₁ / 2)) * (fmax hf - fmin hf)
f_tilde_c_eq: f_tilde c = fmax hf + (f c - fmin hf + (fmax hf - fmin hf))
sum_dist_pos: 0 < f c - fmin hf + (fmax hf - fmin hf)
f_tilde_c_gt_max_f: fmax hf < f_tilde c
hf_tilde: Continuous f_tilde
nconst_f_tilde: ¬Constant f_tilde
x':= compact_argmax hf_tilde: α
δ: ℝ
δ_pos: δ > 0
hδ: ∀ x ∉ Metric.ball c (ε₁ / 2), dist (f_tilde x) (f_tilde x') > δ
h: ∀ ε > 0, ∃ N, ∀ n ≥ N, measure_dist_max A hf_tilde δ ↑n ≤ ε
N: ↑nstar
N_succ:= ⟨↑N + 1, ⋯⟩: ↑nstar
hN: (A.μ f_tilde ↑N_succ) {u | dist (Tuple.max (f_tilde ∘ u)) (fmax hf_tilde) > δ} ≤ ε₂ / (2 * ↑↑N₁) / 2
hc: ε₂ / (2 * ↑↑N₁) ≤ (A.μ f ↑N_succ) {u | ∀ (i : Fin ↑N_succ), u i ∉ Metric.ball c (ε₁ / 2)}
u: Fin ↑N_succ → α
hu: u ∈ {u | ∀ (i : Fin ↑N_succ), u i ∉ Metric.ball c (ε₁ / 2)}
mpr.intro.intro.intro.intro.intro.intro.intro.intro.intro
u ∈ {u | dist (Tuple.max (f_tilde ∘ u)) (fmax hf_tilde) > δ}
